# ML Model Artifacts Directory

This directory contains trained ML models and preprocessing pipelines.

## Files stored here after training:
- `xgb_model_app.joblib` - XGBoost app model (13 non-invasive features)
- `xgb_model_clinical.joblib` - XGBoost clinical model (22 features with labs)
- `dfu_model_best.pth` - DFU detection pre-trained model
- `preprocessor.joblib` - Feature preprocessing pipeline

## Generate artifacts:
```bash
cd backend/ml
python train_model_optimized.py    # Generates XGBoost models
python train_dfu_model_optimized.py # Generates DFU model
```

All artifacts are referenced in `app/services/`:
- `ml_predictor.py` loads XGBoost models
- `dfu_classifier.py` loads DFU detection model
